STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Ricky Dean RYAN, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-2031 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 19, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Ricky Dean Ryan appeals after a jury found him guilty of three drug-related charges. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
